title: Ep. 379 - The War On Facts
description:
Pete Buttigieg is taking fire from the Left for suggesting that kids in the inner city don't have good role models. Also, a journalist was suspended from Twitter for sharing verifiable facts about the alleged anti-trans "hate crime epidemic." And what is the all time worst Christmas present? Date: 11-26-2019
